		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There's no pictures of its inside that I can find, so I can't help with that question, but I'm confident that you could desolder whatever's there and replace it with a modern CIC.<br /><br />You could also just disable both the lock and stunner, which seems a little easier to me.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


