	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Oddly enough, my Honey Bee adapter actually <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=39170#p39170" class="postlink">had a spot on the board for a CIC</a>, wired identically to a real NES cart. After pulling out the badly-soldered mishmash of a &quot;stunner&quot; circuit, I dropped in a CIC from an old Tag Team Pro Wrestling cart, and it worked just fine.<br /><br />I wonder if they had plans for a CIC clone, or if they knew people would do this mod themselves?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


